title: Dogbowl Discography (1987-1995)
description:
Discography of Singer/Songwriter Dogbowl. Contains the two albums he composed with the band King Missile and his solo work up until 1993 + his two collaborations with producer and composer Mark Kramer (of Bongwater, B.A.L.L., etc.).

contains: 
(1987) King Missile: Fluting on the Hump
(1988) King Missile: They
(1989) Tit!... (An Opera)
(1991) Cyclops Nuclear Submarine Captain
(1992) Flan
(1993) Project Success
(1993) w/ Mark Kramer: Hot Day in Waco
(1995) w/ Mark Kramer: Gunsmoke
